As I=E2=80=99ve previewed before, the NFL commissioner and the league have
long fantasized about the billion-dollar possibilities of eliminating anoth=
er preseason contest and adding an 18th regular season game. Murmurs emanat=
ing from New Orleans suggest that the public negotiations have begun.

John Ourand ( https://puck.news/author/john-ourand/?utm_campaign=3DThe+Vars=
ity+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%282%2F6%2F25%29&utm_content=3DThe+Varsity+-+SUBSCRIBERS+=
